The paper applies natural language processing techniques (word embeddings) and deep neural networks to predict stock price movements using financial news. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and deep learning (cs.DL).
